# Tailwind & Styling

## Setup (this project)

- Tailwind v4 via `@import "tailwindcss"` in `app/globals.css`
- Design tokens in `:root` and `@theme inline` — extend tokens there, not scattered magic values

```css
@theme inline {
  --color-brand: #...;
}
```

## Class Patterns

- Mobile-first: base styles, then `sm:`, `md:`, `lg:` breakpoints
- Group related utilities: layout → spacing → typography → color → state
- Use `dark:` variants consistently with existing `prefers-color-scheme` tokens

## Do

- Reuse token classes (`bg-background`, `text-foreground`) over hardcoded hex in components
- Use `flex`/`grid` for layout; avoid absolute positioning unless necessary
- Prefer `gap-*` over margin hacks between siblings

## Avoid

- `@apply` in component files — keep utilities in JSX unless a global primitive is justified
- Arbitrary values (`w-[437px]`) without a design reason
- Inline `style={{}}` when Tailwind covers the case

## Responsive & Motion

- Respect `prefers-reduced-motion` for animations
- Touch targets: minimum ~44×44px on interactive elements
